   5. `row2 = crop(tb, (2,0), (1, width(I)))` – third row.  
   6. `rev_tb = vconcat(vconcat(row2, row1), row0)` – reversed top block.  
   7. `O = vconcat(vconcat(tb, zm), rev_tb)` – final output.

